    <div class="container">
        <h1>How to Open a Door: A Super Detailed Guide</h1>
        <p>Follow these carefully crafted steps to open a door successfully, whether it's your home, office, or anywhere else!</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Approach the Door:</strong> Walk toward the door slowly and steadily, ensuring you are about arm's length away to comfortably reach the handle or knob.</li>
            <li><strong>Identify the Door Handle or Knob:</strong> Look for the door hardware, which is usually located at the mid-height level. It could be a round knob, a lever handle, or sometimes a push bar.</li>
            <li><strong>Check the Door's Lock Status:</strong> Notice if there is a visible lock, a keyhole, or a button indicating if the door is locked or unlocked.</li>
            <li><strong>If the Door is Locked:</strong> Locate your key or access card. Insert the key into the keyhole or swipe the card. Turn the key gently or wait for the access light to indicate unlocking.</li>
            <li><strong>Grip the Handle or Knob Firmly:</strong> Use your dominant hand to grasp the handle completely. For knobs, encircle it with your fingers; for lever handles, wrap your fingers under and thumb on top.</li>
            <li><strong>Turn or Push the Handle:</strong> For knobs, rotate it clockwise or counterclockwise until you feel the latch disengage. For levers, push down firmly until the latch retracts.</li>
            <li><strong>Apply Gentle Pressure on the Door:</strong> After the latch disengages, push or pull the door slowly depending on which side it opens. Use your body weight if necessary but avoid sudden force.</li>
            <li><strong>Walk Through the Doorway:</strong> Once the door is open wide enough, proceed forward through the doorway, ensuring the door is clear of obstructions.</li>
            <li><strong>Close the Door if Needed:</strong> Behind you, gently pull or push the door until it shuts securely. Listen for the click of the latch to confirm it's closed.</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="tip">Tip: Always be mindful of others behind or near the door when you open it to avoid accidents.</div>
    </div>
